commitResults.messageTitle: refactor: Make logo and section bar text final
refactor: Make greeting and goodbye as methods
refactor: Shift task related code to Task class
feat: Add task marking and unmarking
commitResults.messageBody:
Introduces functionality to mark and unmark tasks and track the status
of tasks.

Task listing now reflects status of the task on top of description.

Basic error handling added to deal with `mark` and `unmark` commands
not having a compulsory task number supplied to it.

commitResults.messageTitle: misc: Change name from Duke to AnonBot
commitResults.messageBody:
Renames the program.

Also changes the test scripts and documenataion to reflect
the new changes.

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor: Create Task Manager to manage Tasks

commitResults.messageBody:
Reintroduced functionalities as classes

* CommandManager - Processes the user's inputs as commands
* Parser - Handles Parsing related activities
* Status - Enum file containing status codes
* Ui - Functionalities relating to interating with user

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor: Split User input into command and argument

commitResults.messageBody:
* Now Checks for empty user input
* User inputs now split into Command and optional argument
* Checks the argument associated with `mark` and `unmark` commands
to make sure it is correctly supplied
